@startuml
title Activity: Evidence Chain of Custody

start
:Discover/Collect Evidence;
:Tag with Unique ID;
:Document Location/Time;
:Place in Evidence Bag;
:Sign Custody Log;
:Transport to Evidence Room;
:Evidence Clerk Receives;
:Log in Evidence System;
:Store in Secure Location;
repeat
  :Check-out for Analysis;
  :Return after Analysis;
repeat while (Analysis Complete?) is (No)
->Yes;
:Final Disposition;
stop
